metadata.description: Doodlin Town is a 9,999 NFTs project that teaches us to enjoy life in every sense. They promote friendship and enjoyability to see the world. Doodlins know no fear and nothing worries them. They’re always hungry for new experiences. Their main feature and the motivation behind every course of action they pursue, is pure curiosity. Indeed, they do not care at all for money. That’s why they give away ETH to their holders every week. They are very happy in their village; but Doodlins would like someone to adopt them, either just for a term or on a permanent basis, since they long to shower gifts on their owners, to cook for them and give them affection. Doodlins don’t expect nor ask for anything in return; it’s in their nature to share.
